(19, '8a7baa68-e091-498e-821c-fed64230e12f', 'c8d8ada8-bbb0-4b1c-a2bd-5f26321ebd87', 'b673ff04cf4b2', '<p><img width=\"256\" src=\"/assets/upload_image/4c789a4852f2201dcff097051e959fd44605426f.jpeg\" v:shapes=\"_x0000_i1025\" id=\"isPasted\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"></p><p>Pada tahap reaksi X &nbsp; Y diketahui nilai konstanta laju reaksinya sebesar 5&times;10-3 &nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" class=\"wrs_chemistry\"><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">M</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>.&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" class=\"wrs_chemistry\"><msup><mi>detik</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>. Jika konsentrasi awal X adalah 0,4 M, maka tentukan konsentrasi X setelah 1000 detik!</p><p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>', '2.0 ', '1.0 ', '0.5 ', '0.2 ', '0.1', '96587b45876f47c6df57f4462c0c2334', '<p id=\"isPasted\"><strong>J</strong><strong>awab:&nbsp;E</strong></p><p>Dari data nilai konstanta laju reaksinya sebesar <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" class=\"wrs_chemistry\"><mn>5</mn><mo>&#160;</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">x</mi><mo>&#160;</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mo>&#160;</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">M</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>. <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" class=\"wrs_chemistry\"><msup><mi>detik</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>&nbsp;diketahui bahwa orde reaksinya adalah orde 2. Sehingga untuk mencari waktu paruhnya dihitung sebagai berikut:</p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>t</mi><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp;= <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><msub><mi>M</mi><mi>o</mi></msub><