(20, '8a7baa68-e091-498e-821c-fed64230e12f', 'c4dde305-7508-4e5c-acdd-7be0af66e133', '0609dc93e8375', '<p id=\"isPasted\"></p><p>Perhatikan rangkaian kapasitor berikut ini!</p><img width=\"273\" src=\"/assets/upload_image/b63a87c925ee82a7530c76739f4a67492e64bf9d.jpeg\" v:shapes=\"_x0000_i1025\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><p></p><p>Mula-mula kapasitor C1 &nbsp; = 10&micro;F dihubungkan ke baterai melalui saklar S (kontak ke titik 1). Setelah waktu yang cukup lama, kemudian kapasitor C1 &nbsp;dihubungkan dengan kapasitor C2 = 2 &micro;F &nbsp;yang belum bermuatan melalui saklar S (kontak ke titik 2). Setelah waktu yang cukup lama, muatan yang yang tersimpan pada kapasitor C1 dan C2 kini masing-masing menjadi &hellip;</p><p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>', '60 µC dan 60 µC', '70 µC dan 50 µC', '80 µC dan 40 µC', '90 µC dan 30 µC', '100 µC dan 20 µC', '96587b45876f47c6df57f4462c0c2334', '<p id=\"isPasted\">Q1&nbsp;=&nbsp;C1.V&nbsp;=&nbsp;10&micro;.(12)&nbsp;=&nbsp;120&nbsp;&micro;C</p><p>Setelah &nbsp;&nbsp;dilepaskan &nbsp; &nbsp;kontaknya &nbsp;&nbsp;dengan &nbsp;&nbsp;baterai &nbsp;&nbsp;dan</p><p>dihubungkan&nbsp;ke&nbsp;C2,</p><p>Ctot &nbsp;=&nbsp;C1&nbsp;+&nbsp;C2&nbsp;=&nbsp;10&nbsp;+&nbsp;2 =&nbsp;12 &micro;F</p><p>Qtot&nbsp;=&nbsp;Q1&nbsp;=&nbsp;120&nbsp;&micro;C</p><p>V&rsquo;&nbsp;=&nbsp;Qtot/Ctot&nbsp;=&nbsp;120/12&nbsp;=&nbsp;10&nbsp;volt</p><p>Q1&rsquo;&nbsp;=&nbsp;C1.V&rsquo;&nbsp;=&nbsp;10&micro;.10&nbsp;=&nbsp;100&nbsp;&micro;C</p><p>Q2&rsquo; = C2.V&rsquo; = 2&micro;.10 = 20 &micro;C</p><p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>', '1', '2022-04-30 03:27:46', '2022-04-30 03:27:46'),
(21, '8a7baa68-e091-498e-821c-fed64230e12f', 'c4dde305-7508-4e5c-acdd-7be0af66e133', '2fd193ef7d720', '<p id=\"isPasted\">Sebuah partikel bermuatan dilepas dari keadaan rehat di suatu &nbsp;tempat &nbsp;yang &nbsp;mengandung &nbsp;medan &nbsp;listrik &nbsp;konstan dan medan magnet konstan. Jika arah dua medan ini paralel, lintasan gerak partikel akan berbentuk &hellip;</p><p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>', 'lingkaran', 'parabola', 'helix', 'cycloid', 'garis lurus', '91440c32bd1a49d731350486eadd5f05', '<p id=\"isPasted\"><strong>J</strong><strong>awab:&nbsp;E</strong></p><p>Partikel &nbsp;bermuatan &nbsp;q &nbsp;yang &nbsp;diletakkan &nbsp;dalam &nbsp;medan</p><p>listrik&nbsp;(E)&nbsp;akan&nbsp;mengalami&nbsp;gaya&nbsp;listrik&nbsp;sebesar</p><p>Flistrik&nbsp;=&nbsp;q.E</p><p>dengan&nbsp;arah&nbsp;sejajar&nbsp;medan&nbsp;listrik.&nbsp;Sehingga&nbsp;partikel&nbsp;ini</p><p>akan&nbsp;bergerak paralel&nbsp;kedua&nbsp;medan&nbsp;ini.&nbsp;Gaya&nbsp;magnet tidak&nbsp;ada&nbsp;karena&nbsp;sudut&nbsp;antara&nbsp;kecepatan partikel&nbsp;v&nbsp;dan arah&nbsp;medan&nbsp;magnet&nbsp;B, &theta;&nbsp;=&nbsp;0o&nbsp;atau&nbsp;&theta;&nbsp;=&nbsp;180o.</p><p>Fmagnet = qvB sin &theta; = 0</p><p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>', '1', '2022-04-30 03:30:39', '2022-04-30 03:30:39'),
(22, '8a7baa68-e091-498e-821c-fed64230e12f', 'c4dde305-7508-4e5c-acdd-7be0af66e133', '9065d50b03416', '<p id=\"isPasted\">Diagram&nbsp;di&nbsp;bawah&nbsp;ini&nbsp;menggambarkan baterai&nbsp;yang&nbsp;akan diisi&nbsp;menggunakan generator&nbsp;G.&nbsp;Generator&nbsp;memiliki tegangan&nbsp;terminal&nbsp;120&nbsp;volt&nbsp;ketika&nbsp;<em>mencharge&nbsp;</em>dengan arus</p><p>10&nbsp;A.&nbsp;Baterai&nbsp;memiliki&nbsp;ggl&nbsp;100&nbsp;volt&nbsp;dan&nbsp;hambatan dalam&nbsp;1 ohm.&nbsp;Agar&nbsp;proses&nbsp;charging&nbsp;berlangsung pada&nbsp;kuat&nbsp;arus sebesar&nbsp;10&nbsp;ampere,&nbsp;resistansi R&nbsp;harus&nbsp;diatur&nbsp;sehingga bernilai&nbsp;&hellip;</p><p><img width=\"166\" src=\"/assets/upload_image/4c944796c540b22a89845071a63fbb0fa32e9c4c.jpeg\" v:shapes=\"_x0000_i1025\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"></p><p><br></p><p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>', '0,1 ohm ', '0,5 ohm ', '1,0 ohm', '5,0 ohm', '10,0 ohm', '91440c32bd1a49d731350486eadd5f05', '<p id=\"isPasted\"><strong>J</strong><strong>awab:&nbsp;C</strong></p><p>Dengan &nbsp; &nbsp;menggunakan &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;hukum &nbsp; &nbsp;Kirchoff &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;mengenai</p><p>tegangan:</p><p>Vxx&nbsp;=&nbsp;-VG&nbsp;+&nbsp;E +&nbsp;i(r&nbsp;+&nbsp;R)&nbsp;=&nbsp;0</p><p>120&nbsp;+&nbsp;100 +&nbsp;10(1&nbsp;+&nbsp;R) =&nbsp;0</p><p>R = 1 ohm</p><p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>', '1', '2022-04-30 03:33:08', '2022-04-30 03:33:08'),
