exposed to the dangerous chemical compound,&rdquo; JPKL head Roro Daras wrote in the petition.</p><p>The&nbsp;Indonesian&nbsp;Food&nbsp;Testing&nbsp;Laboratory Network&nbsp;(JLPPI)&nbsp;echoed&nbsp;the&nbsp;petitioners,&nbsp;saying&nbsp;that&nbsp;the&nbsp;country&nbsp;had&nbsp;insufficient regulations&nbsp;on&nbsp;BPA&nbsp;in&nbsp;food&nbsp;packaging.</p><p>Several countries, such as Austria, Belgium and Canada, have prohibited producers from using BPA in making food contact plastics since 2011.</p><p>In a statement issued in January, the BPOM said studies conducted in the past five years had shown that the migration &mdash; or the transfer of chemical substances from food contact materials into food &mdash; of BPA in the refillable water gallon was under 10 micrograms per kilogram of plastic.</p><p>In&nbsp;2019,&nbsp;the&nbsp;agency&nbsp;issued&nbsp;a&nbsp;regulation&nbsp;limiting&nbsp;the&nbsp;migration&nbsp;of&nbsp;BPA to&nbsp;600&nbsp;micrograms&nbsp;per&nbsp;kg&nbsp;of&nbsp;polycarbonate&nbsp;plastic packaging.</p><p>The BPOM cited several studies from the European Food Safety Authority (EFSA) that highlighted the minimum effect of BPA on humans because data showed that the substance&rsquo;s exposure was too low to affect one&rsquo;s health.</p><p>It also cited information obtained from other studies conducted by international organizations, concluding that the usage of refillable water containers made of polycarbonate does not increase BPA migration levels in water.</p><p><br></p><p id=\"isPasted\"><strong>The main information of the text will be closely related to &hellip;</strong></p><p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>', 'labit', 'health', 'lifestyle', 'environment', 'ecosystem', '1c78b5137117db1dd0dbba994c972b4f', '<p id=\"isPasted\"><strong>J</strong><strong>awab:&nbsp;B</strong></p><p>Informasi &nbsp;utama &nbsp;wacana &nbsp;akan &nbsp;berkaitan &nbsp;erat &nbsp;dengan Kesehatan (=health), kita simpulkan dari awal hingga akhir paragraf.</p><p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>', '1', '2022-05-01 00:15:24', '2022-05-01 00:17:07');

